snippet.title: Gone Home - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: To celebrate the release of the game, we've made a little trailer showcasing the premise of the mystery, and some of the wonderful reviews the game has gotten. Thank you so much to everyone who has played, and will play, Gone Home.
